# Simsir, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Simsir (; , Simsara) is a rural locality (a selo) in Osmanyurtovsky Selsoviet, Khasavyurtovsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:  There are 10 streets.
Geography
Simsir is located 9&nbsp;km northwest of Khasavyurt (the district's administrative centre) by road. Osmanyurt is the nearest rural locality.
